File:

failure.json

Schema:

{
  "runId": "",
  "artifactName": "",
  "failureType": "",
  "failureMessage": "",
  "failureTimestamp": ""
}

---

24. Failure Types

Allowed values:

CONFIGURATION_FAILURE

MANIFEST_FAILURE

HOST_VALIDATION_FAILURE

DOWNLOAD_FAILURE

DEPLOYMENT_FAILURE

SANITY_FAILURE

EXECUTION_FAILURE

VALIDATION_FAILURE

TIMEOUT_FAILURE

No additional failure types permitted.

---

25. Notification Architecture

Notification generation occurs after:

Artifact Failure

Execution Completion

Summary Generation

---

26. Failure Notification Contract

Schema:

{
  "runId": "",
  "artifactName": "",
  "failureType": "",
  "failureMessage": "",
  "awxJobId": "",
  "awxJobUrl": ""
}

---

27. Completion Notification Contract

Schema:

{
  "runId": "",
  "overallStatus": "",
  "totalArtifacts": 0,
  "successfulArtifacts": 0,
  "failedArtifacts": 0,
  "durationSeconds": 0
}

---

28. Notification Trigger Rules

Failure:

Immediately

Completion:

After execution summary generation

Summary:

After all artifacts complete

---

29. Report Retention

Default:

report_retention_days: 30

After retention period:

Archive
or
Delete

Based on environment policy.

---

30. Checkpoint Retention

Default:

checkpoint_retention_days: 15

Expired checkpoints may be removed.

---

31. Data Ownership

Artifact Report:

Reporting Role

Validation Report:

Validation Role

Summary Report:

Reporting Role

Checkpoint Files:

Checkpoint Role

---

32. Error Handling Rules

Report generation failure:

Do not fail execution

Log warning

Continue notifications

Checkpoint generation failure:

Fail execution

Resume capability compromised

---

33. Coding Rules

All JSON reports:

Pretty printed

UTF-8

Valid JSON

All timestamps:

ISO-8601 UTC

Example:

2025-05-18T10:15:00Z

---

